snippet.title: Radiant Exodus | Free Horror FPS UFO Mutants Game | Gameplay 2 | Unreal Engine 5.2
snippet.description:
As Sarah Caldwell find a weapon by the ammo store, she rescues herself from being slaughtered by the mutants, as she progress in the streets of Gleam City to clear our more mutant threats

The game is available to download for free on itch.io:
https://horrawr.itch.io/radiant-exodus
